    "Metadata": {
        "Id": "b268e577-f775-4746-b5d9-8e527449d773",
        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "Search (Un)Warrant",
        "Location": "LOCATION_NORTHAMERICA",
        "PublicId": "122335331953",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/skunk/scene_skunk.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 856b2aa2-e224-48c3-b890-01fdf4dba6de).Image",
        "Description": "Good mornign 47, your targets are a group of five conspirators involved in covering up the murders of a cab driver and its passanger recently found by a creek in Vermont, the local police department deemed the death an accident, blaming it on the taxi crashing, but the scene looked rather fishy and the autopsies contradicted the claims made by the local Sheriff.\r\rOur client, or better said clients, are a group of freelance investigators looking into the case, they&#39;ve given up on attempting to work with the Sheriff after he avoided all questions regarding the case and have decided their list of culprits must be punished by other means, they&#39;ve also asked that you retrieve what they are most sure were weapons used to commit the assault.\r\rGood luck 47, I&#39;ll leave you to prepare.",
